Placeholder: The Warrant Oak

A placeholder encounter for the Warrant Oak arc.

choices:

* Explore = Search the hideout [requires quality faction.exiles 5]
    @if check combat medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +upgrade_pack 2
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Negotiate = Talk your way through [requires quality faction.exiles 5]
    @if check negotiation medium {
        You find something valuable.
        +upgrade_pack 2
        +finish_dungeon
    } @else {
        It doesn't go well.
        +add_condition injured
        +finish_dungeon
    }

* Depart = Leave this place behind
    You decide this is not the time. You turn and walk away.
    +flee_dungeon
